## PART 7 — SERVER ARCHITECTURE

```
inkframe/
├── app/                          # Next.js frontend
│   ├── page.tsx                  # Main editor
│   ├── v/[projectId]/page.tsx    # Published viewer
│   ├── dashboard/[id]/analytics  # Analytics
│   └── api/
│       ├── agent/route.ts        # Main agent endpoint (streaming)
│       ├── upload/route.ts       # File uploads
│       ├── publish/route.ts      # Publish interactive
│       └── export/route.ts       # Trigger MP4 export
│
├── lib/
│   ├── agents/
│   │   ├── router.ts             # Intent classification
│   │   ├── director.ts           # Multi-scene planning
│   │   ├── scene-maker.ts        # Layer generation
│   │   ├── editor.ts             # Surgical edits
│   │   ├── dop.ts                # Global style/timing
